{"tid":2278763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［武肺討論］如果係你 你會點打定唔打","createTime":"2020-11-09T10:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T13:12:22.000Z","uid":100493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac906b25f0209ace066652c9515adc9a863a8ec","tid":2278763,"uid":100493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"同你講<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界有疫苗可以擋到武肺<br />\n<br />\n但係每年打一針大約要成十皮野<br />\n<br />\n亦變相個社會開始慢慢有窮人同有錢人既標籤<br />\n<br />\n假如你每個月得三皮野收入，你會：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 俾錢打疫苗<br />\n<br />\n2/ 唔打 戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n3/ 唔戴口罩 扮自己有打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有細路哥既你 又會唔會俾個仔打番針 定係叫佢戴口罩算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想睇大家會點諗 純粹學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904092a9dae86582b98decb4f9f28423ba5d67c1","tid":2278763,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"打左窮死<br />\n唔打病死<br />\n文明社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d85c8f6dd178d33974046c7b197349ec56996f","tid":2278763,"uid":100493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"1/ 俾錢打疫苗"},{"pid":"b9e5e21bf8d40d3eeba8aba40cdd92eaca25fe01","tid":2278763,"uid":100493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"2/ 唔打 戴口罩"},{"pid":"86ef92f9e97651c95a421a446bf03fa1d1f8ab9a","tid":2278763,"uid":100493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"3/ 唔戴口罩 扮自己有打"},{"pid":"4260c6afb1e30bcd0b3e0c228ee3006b414af686","tid":2278763,"uid":100493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:12:22.000Z","msg":"即刻出左疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/to